OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'open to conversation' on
OL,4,Cdevolving more powers, FM says
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fproposed a face-to-face meeting with
OL,8,Fthe leaders of the devolved
OL,9,Fgovernments next month after
OL,10,Fconfirming he would be "open to a
OL,11,Fconversation" about devolving more
OL,12,Fpowers from Westminster.
OL,14,FSir Keir put forward the idea of a
OL,15,Fmeeting in June during a phone call
OL,16,Fwith Plaid Cymru's newly-installed
OL,17,FFirst Minister of Wales Rhun ap
OL,18,FIorwerth.
OL,26,@rD@XOUsD@MO]
