PN,46404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778951200
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'open to conversation' on
OL,4,Cdevolving more powers, FM says
OL,6,FOthers familiar with the conversation
OL,7,Fsay the Welsh Government's account is
OL,8,Fbroadly accurate but doesn't mention
OL,9,Fthat the First Minister brought up the
OL,10,Fmatter of independence. They express
OL,11,Fsurprise that this was mentioned in
OL,12,Fthe first conversation with the Prime
OL,13,FMinister.
OL,15,FThe readout also said the First
OL,16,FMinister sought co-operation from Sir
OL,17,FKeir "on the impact of the conflict in
OL,18,Fthe Middle East on the cost of living".
OL,26,@yD@FOUzD@fO]
