CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1778951200
OL,3,CKeir Starmer 'open to conversation' on
OL,4,Cdevolving more powers, FM says
OL,6,FMr ap Iorwerth also had phone calls on
OL,7,FThursday with Scottish First Minister
OL,8,FJohn Swinney and First Minister of
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Michelle O'Neill.
OL,11,FAfter the meeting, the First Minister
OL,12,Fshared on X: "The bonds across these
OL,13,Fisles are strong, and I look forward
OL,14,Fto working closely on issues of shared
OL,15,Finterest, and meeting up in person in
OL,16,Fthe near future."
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
